summary: This season's promo is so around both Maisie/Sophie/Arya/Sansa. I love Mophie. But I'd really prefer Sophie/Sansa solo. Even on...
question: This season's promo is so around both Maisie/Sophie/Arya/Sansa. I love Mophie. But I'd really prefer Sophie/Sansa solo. Even on press junket, Kit and Emilia are the only actors who were interviewed alone, don't understand why others don't do that. I want to focus on one character. But I think it's only because they're leads. Also photoshoots trying to make them a team. I can't see it at all. Not after the shit Arya was doing in s7. I really don't want this forced sisterhood.
answer: Same anon. I’m glad they’re together since they’re so close but I want Sansa centric interviews and photoshoots. Honestly after they spent all of their scenes in season 1 fighting and then spent nearly of their scenes in S7 with Arya threatening to harm her, we’re supposed to buy that they’re close and they love and respect one another?
